    {
      "id": "bfs-detail",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 162,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "1. Build graph from CHANNEL_ANNOUNCE msgs\n2. Edge weight = 1 / trust_score(peer)\n   (higher trust → lower cost)\n3. BFS from source to destination\n4. Filter: channel.remaining >= amount\n5. Return shortest weighted path\n\ndef find_route(src, dst, amount, graph):",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1E40AF",
      "roughness": 0
    },

