      "width": 340,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "If any hop cannot fulfill:\n• Timeout expired (t=0)\n• Insufficient channel balance\n• Peer offline\n→ HTLC_CANCEL propagates back to source\n→ No funds are transferred at any hop",
